Join MAC VIVA GLAM in putting your money where your mouth is with five shades that give back 100% to supporting equal rights and healthy futures for ALL.

Just picked up @thegirljt to #GRWMAC for NYC Pride 🏳️‍🌈👑💋. Here’s everything the City Princess wore for her next-level set:

ON THE LIPS 💋
Lip Pencil in Chestnut

Lipglass Clear

ON THE FACE ✨

#MACLovesPride #Pride #PrideMonth #NYCPride

NEW YORK CITY! 🗽🌈 We hit the parade route in full #MAC style – celebrating love, individuality and the beauty of our LGBTQIA+ community. With bold lips, and our larger-than-life Lipstick truck, we’re committed to driving change with five iconic VIVA GLAM shades that give back 100% to support equality and brighter futures for all.

Where should our Pride float pull up next?

#MACLovesPride #MACVIVAGLAM
